<section id="about">


    <section class="section"  >
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>How SkillConnect Pro became the leading platform for local service connections</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h3>From Vision to Reality</h3>
                    <p>Founded in 2025 by Adarsh Pandey, Worker-Finder emerged from a simple yet powerful idea: to create a platform that makes finding reliable local service professionals as easy as ordering food delivery. Adarsh recognized the challenges homeowners face when searching for trustworthy carpenters, electricians, and plumbers, while also understanding the struggles skilled workers encounter in finding consistent work.</p>
                    <p>What began as a small startup has grown into a comprehensive platform serving thousands of customers and professionals across multiple cities. Our rigorous vetting process, innovative matching algorithm, and commitment to customer satisfaction have set us apart in the industry.</p>
                    <p>Today, Worker-Finder continues to innovate, with plans to expand to new service categories and implement AI-powered recommendations to further improve the user experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521791136064-7986c2920216?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Team working together">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

