    <!-- Strategy Section -->
    <section class="section" style="background-color: #f1f5f9;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Our Strategic Approach</h2>
                <p>How we're building the future of local service connections</p>
            </div>
            <div class="strategy-steps">
                <div class="strategy-step">
                    <div class="strategy-content">
                        <h3>Rigorous Vetting Process</h3>
                        <p>We've developed a comprehensive 5-step verification process that includes identity verification, license checks, skills assessment, background screening, and customer feedback analysis. This ensures only the most qualified professionals join our platform.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-step">
                    <div class="strategy-content">
                        <h3>Smart Matching Technology</h3>
                        <p>Our proprietary algorithm considers over 20 factors including location, availability, skillset, pricing, and customer ratings to make the perfect match for each job requirement.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-step">
                    <div class="strategy-content">
                        <h3>Continuous Quality Improvement</h3>
                        <p>We collect feedback after every completed job and use this data to improve our matching system, identify training opportunities for professionals, and enhance the overall user experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-step">
                    <div class="strategy-content">
                        <h3>Community Building Initiatives</h3>
                        <p>We host regular workshops and networking events for our professionals, provide business development resources, and create opportunities for skill enhancement to help them grow their businesses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="strategy-step">
                    <div class="strategy-content">
                        <h3>Technology Roadmap</h3>
                        <p>Our future plans include AI-powered job estimates, augmented reality for remote assessments, blockchain-based credential verification, and IoT integration for predictive maintenance alerts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

